citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 8:53 am on
01/22/2016.
APHIS ACI contacted the licensee via telephone and it was determined that no one was available to go on an
inspection.
Additional Inspectors
Tims Tanya, Assistant Director
